(13, 1, '2015-03-29 17:07:22', '2015-03-29 17:07:22', '<h3 class="centered-text">Working together to protect your business</h3>\r\n<p>As specialists in supplying Lenovo and IBM IT support, Software Services and Maintenance Contracts since 2004, we know how integral your IT system is to your business. That’s why a commitment to protect your hardware and software assets is at the heart of ours. Our commitment to supporting our customers’ businesses has seen us become certified Lenovo specialists and a market-leading outsourced sales and marketing operation for IBM Global Services, supplying IBM ServicePacs and ServiceSuite to IBM business partners, distributors and end-users across the globe.</p>', 'About', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2015-04-25 17:56:30', '2015-04-25 17:56:30', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?page_id=13', 5, 'page', '', 0),
