nnual prepaid invoicing</li>\r\n<li>delivered with a renewal reminder</li>\r\n<li>delivered with the option to buy a Committed Fix – where engineers are guaranteed to answer call-outs within 4 hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>The IBM Service Suite Maintenance Contract could be the ideal option if you:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list blue">\r\n<li>have older hardware</li>\r\n<li>own hardware not supported by the Service Pack</li>\r\n<li>run high-end servers</li>\r\n<li>have multiple hardware systems</li>\r\n<li>maintain a custom-built system</li>\r\n<li>require a customised level of service</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</header></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row blue-btns">\r\n<div class="small-12 columns"><footer class="insets-footer">\r\n<p>Want to know more? <a href="#">Read our FAQs</a>.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Like more advice or still wondering whether the IBM Service Suite Maintenance Contract will meet your needs?<br />Call us on <a href="tel:">XXXX XXXXXXXX</a> or <a href="mailto:">email us now</a>.</strong></p>\r\n<p><a class="read-more" href="#"><span class="inner">Webchat now?</span></a></p>\r\n</footer></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="skewed-bg"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', 'Option 2 - IBM Service Suite Maintenance Contract', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '218-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-20 19:34:45', '2015-04-20 19:34:45', '', 218, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/uncategorised/218-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(248, 1, '2015-04-20 20:22:50', '2015-04-20 20:22:50', '<p>After studying French and German at Nottingham University, Jim started his career working for a publishing company selling into the German market before making the move to travel and work overseas, living for periods in Sydney, Santiago and crossing Russia on the Trans Mongolian Express.</p>\r\n<p>Combining his love of travel and business, Jim set up Europlus Direct in 2004 with one vision; to make it simple for businesses to trade internationally.  With 8 global operations across Australasia, Africa, America and Europe, one of Jim’s proudest moments was when Europlus Direct won the Queen’s Award for International Trade in 2008 and 2013, taking him one step closer to achieving his goal.</p>\r\n<p> Outside of the office, Jim loves spending time with the family and when he’s not teaching his children how to play different sports, he enjoys rustling up a barbecue. When time allows, Jim also enters a few cycling Sportives every year and takes to the golf course every now and then – although with more enthusiasm than skill. But he’s working on that.</p>', 'Jim Hart', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jim-hart', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:01:06', '2015-04-23 13:01:06', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_team&#038;p=248', 0, 'cpt_team', '', 0),
