(250, 1, '2015-04-20 20:25:54', '2015-04-20 20:25:54', '<p>As Financial Director of a global business, Rob manages the company’s cash flow, forecasting and budgeting to ensure that our finances run smoothly – in over 42 different currencies!</p>\r\n<p>Rob joined Europlus Direct in 2010 having worked previously in the translation industry at The Big Word and various companies within the advertising industry. Before that he completed a degree in Management and became ACMA qualified.</p>\r\n<p>Rob is a keen traveller, but when he’s not jet-setting, he enjoys many sports, especially football and more recently, golf. </p>', 'Rob Jobbins ACMA CGMA', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rob-jobbins-acma-cgma', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:04:12', '2015-04-23 13:04:12', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_team&#038;p=250', 1, 'cpt_team', '', 0),
