(286, 1, '2015-04-21 08:21:29', '2015-04-21 08:21:29', '<p>Yes, as long as you use genuine IBM parts and they’re installed by an IBM engineer.</p>', 'Is my Maintenance Contract still valid if I modify my IBM hardware?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'is-my-maintenance-contract-still-valid-if-i-modify-my-ibm-hardware', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:33:44', '2015-04-21 13:33:44', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=286', 25, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(287, 1, '2015-04-21 08:22:34', '2015-04-21 08:22:34', '<p>No, ServicePac benefits are only available to the business they’re registered to – but the new owner can buy their own ServicePac for the hardware.</p>', 'If I sell my IBM hardware, can I also transfer my ServicePac?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'if-i-sell-my-ibm-hardware-can-i-also-transfer-my-servicepac', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:34:01', '2015-04-21 13:34:01', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=287', 26, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(288, 1, '2015-04-21 08:23:06', '2015-04-21 08:23:06', '<p>Committed Service is an option that means your agreement will state that an approved engineer will arrive on-site within 4hrs to repair your equipment.</p>', 'What does Committed Service mean?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-does-committed-service-mean', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:34:17', '2015-04-21 13:34:17', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=288', 27, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(289, 1, '2015-04-21 08:23:57', '2015-04-21 08:23:57', '<p>You can tailor your cover to suit your needs and budget, with a choice of cover length (eg. 1 and 2 year cover options), 9 to 5 or 24/7 response and next business day or same day service.</p>', 'What service levels can I choose from?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-service-levels-can-i-choose-from', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:34:34', '2015-04-21 13:34:34', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=289', 28, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(290, 1, '2015-04-21 08:24:39', '2015-04-21 08:24:39', '<p>We’ve been a trusted IBM partner for over 10 years, have over 40 dedicated account managers around the world and can deliver the vital IT business support you need, when you need it.</p>', 'What makes you an approved IBM specialist?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-makes-you-an-approved-ibm-specialist', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:34:52', '2015-04-21 13:34:52', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=290', 29, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(291, 1, '2015-04-21 08:25:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'auto-draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2015-04-21 08:25:45', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&p=291', 0, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(292, 1, '2015-04-21 08:26:35', '2015-04-21 08:26:35', '<p>Absolutely. Simply send us the serial numbers, models and types and we’ll contact you before your current warranty runs out to discuss your renewal options.</p>', 'Can you manage my entire IT system?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-you-manage-my-entire-it-system', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:35:08', '2015-04-21 13:35:08', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=292', 30, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(293, 1, '2015-04-21 08:27:13', '2015-04-21 08:27:13', '<p>Yes. We can put you in touch with dedicated account managers around the world who can help you buy Service Packs in over 130 countries.</p>', 'Can I extend IBM warranties for different hardware in different countries?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-i-extend-ibm-warranties-for-different-hardware-in-different-countries', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:35:24', '2015-04-21 13:35:24', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=293', 31, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(294, 1, '2015-04-21 08:27:57', '2015-04-21 08:27:57', '<p>This is for tax legislation reasons, but you can buy through our global account managers, so the process is simple and straightforward. Please note that if you buy a ServicePac in the UK for a machine and then ship that machine to another country, it cannot be supported and the ServicePac will be invalid.</p>', 'My business is based in the UK, so why do I have to buy ServicePacs for my foreign offices in each individual country?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'my-business-is-based-in-the-uk-so-why-do-i-have-to-buy-servicepacs-for-my-foreign-offices-in-each-individual-country', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:35:41', '2015-04-21 13:35:41', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=294', 32, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(295, 1, '2015-04-21 08:28:48', '2015-04-21 08:28:48', '<p>To keep things nice and simple, you can pay in advance by bank transfer or cheque.</p>', 'How do I pay for ServicePacs, Software Services and Maintenance Contracts?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-do-i-pay-for-servicepacs-software-services-and-maintenance-contracts', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:35:57', '2015-04-21 13:35:57', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=295', 33, 'cpt_question', '', 0);
