(296, 1, '2015-04-21 08:29:32', '2015-04-21 08:29:32', '<p>We welcome a wide range of currencies; sterling, euros, US dollars, Swiss francs and Danish krone.</p>', 'What currencies do you accept?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-currencies-do-you-accept', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:36:18', '2015-04-21 13:36:18', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=296', 34, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(297, 1, '2015-04-21 08:30:00', '2015-04-21 08:30:00', '<p>Yes. Just tell us whether you’d like to deal in sterling, euros, US dollars, Swiss francs and Danish krome and we’ll take care of the rest.</p>', 'Can I keep things simple with one invoice in one currency?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-i-keep-things-simple-with-one-invoice-in-one-currency', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:36:34', '2015-04-21 13:36:34', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=297', 35, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
