(299, 1, '2015-04-21 08:31:24', '2015-04-21 08:31:24', '<p>Simply call <a href="tel:">+44 (0)113 887 8650</a> or email <a href="mailto:worldwidesales@europlusdirect.com">worldwidesales@europlusdirect.com</a></p>', 'How do I get a quote?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-do-i-get-a-quote', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:36:51', '2015-04-21 13:36:51', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=299', 36, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(300, 1, '2015-04-21 08:31:56', '2015-04-21 08:31:56', '<p>When you take out a ServicePac, we’ll give you direct contact details for your local IBM Support Assistant.</p>', 'Who do I call if I need IBM hardware support?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'who-do-i-call-if-i-need-ibm-hardware-support', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:37:17', '2015-04-21 13:37:17', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=300', 37, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(301, 1, '2015-04-21 08:33:29', '2015-04-21 08:33:29', '<p>So that you can fully redeem all the services available in your agreement, your agreement has to be bought in each relevant country. However, with Europlus Direct, our dedicated account managers can help you with an easy registration process, so <a href="#">contact us</a> today.</p>', 'My hardware is in separate countries, do I have to buy support in those countries?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'my-hardware-is-in-separate-countries-do-i-have-to-buy-support-in-those-countries', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:37:35', '2015-04-21 13:37:35', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=301', 38, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(302, 1, '2015-04-21 08:34:34', '2015-04-21 08:34:34', '<p>Please take a look at <a href="#">our map</a> to see what services we offer, where and please <a href="#">contact us</a> if you are unsure.</p>', 'What kind of support is available, worldwide?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-kind-of-support-is-available-worldwide', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:37:52', '2015-04-21 13:37:52', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=302', 39, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(303, 1, '2015-04-21 08:35:39', '2015-04-21 08:35:39', '<p>If you have an IT system that includes machines from other manufacturers, such as Dell, Cisco or HP, then you may need to cover them with our IBM Multi-Manufacturer Support – one simple service that will protect your whole IT system.</p>', 'What is IBM Multi-Manufacturer Support?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-is-ibm-multi-manufacturer-support', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:38:15', '2015-04-21 13:38:15', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=303', 40, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
(304, 1, '2015-04-21 08:36:40', '2015-04-21 08:36:40', '<p>As with all our services, we need to know the serial numbers or ID of each machine so we can provide the right protection. The same applies to machines of manufacturers other than IBM or Lenovo but if you’re unsure, please <a href="#">contact us</a>.</p>', 'How do I know what you will cover?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-do-i-know-what-you-will-cover', '', '', '2015-04-21 13:38:39', '2015-04-21 13:38:39', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_question&#038;p=304', 41, 'cpt_question', '', 0),
