(306, 1, '2015-04-21 08:49:00', '2015-04-21 08:49:00', '<p>One of the key factors in our winning the Best Multilingual Website award in 2004 is our commitment to provide a top-class service to our customers, no matter where they are located. Our multilingual website and our 30 multilingual staff in the UK ensure that communication with our many international clients is never a problem.</p>\r\n', 'Best Multilingual Website 2004', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'best-multilingual-website-2004', '', '', '2015-04-21 19:45:12', '2015-04-21 19:45:12', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_award&#038;p=306', 2, 'cpt_award', '', 0),
