(316, 1, '2015-04-21 10:21:57', '2015-04-21 10:21:57', '<p>We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a new, bright office and an even better international team consisting of nationalities such as German, Italian, Spanish, French, Swedish, Dutch… and English. We have fun social events, an outside south facing dining area and even a masseur coming once a month. (What more could you ask for, right?)</p>\r\n<p>We are a global company with offices in the UK, Australia, USA &amp; Spain and we predict fantastic growth with annual turnover expected to double in the next 12 months. This is a fantastic opportunity to be a part of something special.</p>\r\n<p>Working on behalf of world renowned names in the IT industry our successful teams have won multiple awards including the Queens Award for International Trade (twice!), now in our 10th year in business, the company is expanding again into the USA.</p>\r\n<p>The successful candidate will be expected to develop new business, and nurture relationships with existing clients in France. This is an office-based role with potential opportunity to travel to France, attend external meetings with clients, suppliers and customers. </p>\r\n<p><strong>In order to be successful in this role you will have:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Fluent French and English</li>\r\n<li>Previous sales experience (face to face/telephone)</li>\r\n<li>Previous Customer Service experience</li>\r\n<li>Clear and confident telephone manner</li>\r\n<li>Strong written and oral communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Dynamic, outgoing attitude</li>\r\n<li>Excellent organisational skills</li>\r\n<li>The desire to hit targets and earn commission</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>The role:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Sales of IT services B2B into France (don’t worry, this isn’t a technical role and all training will be given!)</li>\r\n<li>Determining customer requirements and advising on product range, price and alternatives</li>\r\n<li>Assisting customers and providing excellent service</li>\r\n<li>Preparation of quotes, tenders, invoices etc.</li>\r\n<li>Management of customer database</li>\r\n<li>Sales Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<p>To apply, please send your CV to <a href="mailto:anna.ceder@one-global.com">anna.ceder@one-global.com</a></p>\r\n<p>We look forward to hearing from you!</p>\r\n<p>Keywords: French Sales, French Account Manager, Sales Account Manager</p>', 'French Inside Sales Executive', 'We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a new, bright office and an even better international team consisting of nationalities such as German, Italian, Spanish, French, Swedish, Dutch… and English. We have fun social events, an outside south facing dining area and even a masseur coming once a month. (What more could you ask for, right?)', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'french-inside-sales-executive', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:49:00', '2015-04-23 13:49:00', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_career&#038;p=316', 0, 'cpt_career', '', 0),
(317, 1, '2015-04-21 10:25:21', '2015-04-21 10:25:21', '<p><strong>Inside Sales Executive sought for global company with a great working environment and team! </strong></p>\r\n<p>We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a great new office and an even better international team. We are a global company with offices in the UK, Australia, USA &amp; Spain and we predict fantastic growth with annual turnover expected to double in the next 12 months. This is a fantastic opportunity to be a part of something special.</p>\r\n<p>Working on behalf of world renowned names in the IT industry our successful teams have won multiple awards including the Queens Award for International Trade (twice!), now in our 10th year in business, the company is expanding again into the USA.</p>\r\n<p>The successful candidate will be expected to develop new business, and nurture relationships with existing clients. This is an office-based role with potential opportunity to travel to the US, attend external meetings with clients, suppliers and customers. </p>\r\n<p><strong>The role:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Sales of IT services B2B into the USA, this isn’t a technical role and all training will be given.</li>\r\n<li>Determining customer requirements and advising on product range, price and alternatives</li>\r\n<li>Assisting customers and providing excellent service</li>\r\n<li>Preparation of quotes, tenders, invoices etc.</li>\r\n<li>Management of customer database</li>\r\n<li>Sales Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>In order to be successful in this role you will have:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Previous sales experience (face to face/telephone)</li>\r\n<li>Previous Customer Service experience</li>\r\n<li>Clear and confident telephone manner</li>\r\n<li>Strong written and oral communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Dynamic, outgoing attitude</li>\r\n<li>Excellent organisational skills</li>\r\n<li>The desire to hit targets and earn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The shift pattern for this position is; Monday to Friday 2pm – 10pm</p>\r\n<p>If you would like to apply for this position then please email your CV to <a href="mailto:Sharon.craggs@one-global.com">Sharon.craggs@one-global.com</a>, or call me on 01138878367 to discuss further. I look forward to hearing from you.</p>\r\n', 'Inside Sales Executive – US market', 'We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a great new office and an even better international team. We are a global company with offices in the UK, Australia, USA & Spain and we predict fantastic growth with annual turnover expected to double in the next 12 months. This is a fantastic opportunity to be a part of something special.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'inside-sales-executive-us-market', '', '', '2015-04-21 17:25:18', '2015-04-21 17:25:18', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_career&#038;p=317', 0, 'cpt_career', '', 0),
