(353, 1, '2014-03-03 21:08:00', '2014-03-03 21:08:00', '<p>Europlus Direct’s sister company One Global is one of the sponsors for the Lord Mayor’s Cycle Ride linking up the French and German twin cities to Leeds of Dortmund and Lille.   Here is the link: http://www.lordmayorcycleride.co.uk/</p>\r\n<p>CEO, Jim Hart, is doing the European leg of the trip and now has 56 days to train to get himself up to speed.</p>\r\n<p>All in support of Children’s Charity LOFFTY (Leeds Offers Fun For The Young).</p>', 'Europlus Direct’s sister company proud to sponsor Lord Mayor’s European Charity Bike Ride', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'uroplus-directs-sister-company-proud-to-sponsor-lord-mayors-european-charity-bike-ride', '', '', '2015-04-21 21:11:47', '2015-04-21 21:11:47', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_news&#038;p=353', 0, 'cpt_news', '', 0),
