(362, 1, '2013-06-10 21:19:06', '2013-06-10 21:19:06', '<p><img class=" size-large-image wp-image-364 aligncenter" src="http://europlusdirect.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/golf2-600x370.jpg" alt="golf2" width="600" height="370" /></p>\r\n<p>Europlus Direct and One Global have been supporting several good causes throughout the years, our chosen charity for this year is <a href="http://www.linehamfarm.co.uk/pages/about-the-centre.php">Lineham Farm Children’s Centre</a>.</p>\r\n<p>On Wednesday, June 5<sup>th</sup> 2013, we invited our staff and clients to take part in a 18-hole charity golf competition with all monies raised from the event being donated to Lineham Farm.</p>\r\n<p>Nineteen companies, including Wedge Group, Inspire, Barclays &amp; Mazars, just to name a few, took part in the competition.</p>\r\n<p>Prizes were handed out to the winner, runner up and third place, as well as Nearest Pin and Longest drive. And these were the winners:</p>\r\n<p>1st Prize – Julian Wells of Whitecap Consulting<br />2nd Prize – Fraser Priestley of Mellon Bank of NY<br />3rd prize – Dave Eastland of UPS</p>\r\n<p>Nearest Pin – Andrew Charlesworth of Barclays<br />Longest Drive – Chris Reay of Wedge Group</p>\r\n<p><img class=" size-large-image wp-image-363 aligncenter" src="http://europlusdirect.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/golf1-600x370.jpg" alt="golf1" width="600" height="370" /></p>\r\n<p>Following the  golf event there was a raffle and an auction for some great prizes donated by companies taking part: a week’s holiday in one of their Mallorca villas donated by Villa Parade, a bottle of wine dated 1960 donated by Dave Eastland and many more fantastic contributions.</p>\r\n<p>The generosity of everyone involved as well as the perfect golfing weather made this charity golf competition as well as the raffle and auction a fantastic and very successful event. We managed to raise a grand total of (£1500) for Lineham Farm.</p>\r\n<p>A huge Thank You goes to Hollins Hall who provided us with the venue and facilities as well as all the players and those who donated prizes and made donations.</p>\r\n<p>We can’t wait for next year!</p>', 'Europlus Direct and One Global host Charity Golf Competition', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'europlus-direct-and-one-global-host-charity-golf-competition', '', '', '2015-04-21 22:43:08', '2015-04-21 22:43:08', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost/?post_type=cpt_news&#038;p=362', 0, 'cpt_news', '', 0),
